title: CURATED WIND
description: CURATED WIND - is an extensive sound library containing 171 unique files of Wind (Storms, Gusts, Turbulence, Breeze, Gales, Etc.) in varying environments and conditions.
longDescription: CURATED WIND - is an extensive sound library containing 171 unique files of Wind (Storms, Gusts, Turbulence, Breeze, Gales, Etc.) in varying environments and conditions ranging from city streets, back alleys, parks, forests, windows and attics to deserts, plains, mountain tops, tundra and valleys. All of our libraries comply with the Universal Category System metadata naming convention standard. Files are presented in 44.1 kHz / 16 bit (VIDEO GAME).
technicalDetails:
Features:

  •  171 Unique .wav files of Wind in various environments and conditions.
  •  Universal Category System metadata file naming standard.
  •  Royalty-Free.

Number of Audio Waves: 171

Number of Audio Cues: 171

Sample rate / bit rate: 44,100 Hz / 16 Bit

Do Sound FX loop: No

Minutes of audio provided: 305

Supported Development Platforms:

Windows: Yes

Mac: Yes
